OL,3,CMan hides in family's loft after
OL,4,Cbreaking into home on Boxing Day
OL,6,FA man who hid in a loft after breaking
OL,7,Finto a home in Ashford on Boxing Day
OL,8,Fhas been jailed.
OL,10,FPolice were alerted to a burglary in
OL,11,FBoxley shortly after 2am on Friday 26
OL,12,FDecember 2025, after a resident
OL,13,Farrived home to find their house in
OL,14,Fdisarray.
OL,16,FAtony Allen had broken into the
OL,17,Fproperty a few hours earlier, stealing
OL,18,Fcash, jewellery, bank cards, handbags
OL,19,Fand other personal belongings,
OL,20,Fincluding electronic earbuds.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
