PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772651487
OL,3,CMan hides in family's loft after
OL,4,Cbreaking into home on Boxing Day
OL,6,FOfficers tracked the 47-year-old via
OL,7,Fthe ear buds to a nearby address where
OL,8,Fhe was found hiding in a loft.
OL,10,FThe earbuds and several other items
OL,11,Fbelonging to the victims were
OL,12,Frecovered at the scene.
OL,14,FHe admitted to the burglary and was
OL,15,Fsentenced to two and a half years'
OL,16,Fimprisonment on Wednesday 25 February
OL,17,F2026.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
