OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772651487
OL,3,CMan hides in family's loft after
OL,4,Cbreaking into home on Boxing Day
OL,6,FPC Isobel Harper from Kent Police
OL,7,Fsaid: "The impact of Allen's offending
OL,8,Fcannot be underestimated and I am
OL,9,Fpleased he has received a custodial
OL,10,Fsentence.
OL,12,F"The victims in this case were made to
OL,13,Fundergo the trauma of having their
OL,14,Fhouse turned upside down, along with
OL,15,Fthe loss of items that were important
OL,16,Fto them.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
