PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772651487
OL,3,CMan hides in family's loft after
OL,4,Cbreaking into home on Boxing Day
OL,6,F"Everyone has the right to feel safe
OL,7,Fin their home, and I hope the family
OL,8,Fcan begin to recover from this
OL,9,Ffrightening experience now that the
OL,10,Foffender has been brought to justice."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
